text: An Hae-eun (; born 7 May 1963) is a South Korean rowing coxswain. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Coxswains (rowing)
